main event: A military patrol observed a bright white object in the sky that was visible for 7 minutes.
interesting points: The object was observed moving from due south to due southwest, heading at 225 degrees.
The object was as bright as a lightning flash and left a visible vapor trail.
The size and speed of the object were comparable to a jet.
The object was visible at 33 degrees above the horizon at the location of 33 degrees north, 177 degrees west.
The sighting was evaluated as not a threat.
sighted object: a bright white object in the sky
